         <abstract id="aspace_98858fee3d3de210bba9ac84992bfb21">Letters between Sarah Buckingham and family and friends, between other family members, and between family and friends. Among the letters from Clark Nettleton to his sister Mrs. Goodsell is a letterhead of a 1858 view of Saint Paul, Minnesota.</abstract>
